<br>
LDoN Gives everyone a chance go move around explore the inner depths of the zone, working toward a goal.  The thing that everyone I have grouped with has loved is the not staying in one constant spot.  Being a puller you get to see more of the zone and is quite fun, but staying in one spot constantly gets boring real quick.<br>
<br>
Thats my look at LDoN, gets a good mark in my book.<br>
