<br>
Grend: I think the point is just that you weren't around when the expansion offered a sense of, uh, &quot;expanding&quot; the game.<br>
<br>
Kunark added 10 levels to the game, a few spells for each level, a new race, epic weapon quests, a portal to every town in the world if you risked the swim, a slew of dragons, and, what i consider the most important, completely optional &quot;faction grinding&quot; quests that enriched the game, and were not required.<br>
<br>
Velious extended all of that, but offered nothing all that new to the game except, hmm, Tower of Frozen &quot;help my key is on the corpse&quot;, a one-upping of ragefire KSing with stormfeather KSing, literally &quot;required&quot; faction grinding to get any yield in the upper levels, nonrepeating content, and the ever popular tradeskill and ringwar romps.<br>
<br>
I liked velious better than kunark simply out of taste. But in terms of adding new concepts to the game, kunark was the winner. Velious didn't expand so much as extend those ideas that were in place...  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern.showUserPublicProfile?gid=makasmanyheals>Makas Manyheals</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://sendire.mine.nu/isengard/makasavatar.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><span style='color:yellow;'>Tavern Ale Swiller</span></span><br>  Posts: 77<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(9/23/03 5:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3544.topic&index=58>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: um...</span><hr size=1> None of the expansions are better than any other (Well, LoY sucked bad). Original EQ was the stuff. Kerra Isle...Lesser Fay, and The Arena...What new zones own up to those? <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://sendire.mine.nu/isengard/makasblack.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
